          :
  @{bg shine}Change Font...    @{bg background}
          :


@{u}@{b}Change Font@{ub}@{uu}
  A font requeseter will open, allowing you to select a new font.


@{b}Notes:@{ub}
  o By default, OHAC will use the screen's default font.

  o The @{"FONT" link OPT_FONT} and @{"FONTSIZE" link OPT_FONT} startup options may be used to set the font OHAC
    initially uses.
@endnode

@node MENU_SAVE "OHAC Menus:  Project - Snapshot"
